<div id="review_591413641" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/591413641" />
    <a title="Air" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/12077590-air"><img alt="Air" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1466476393p2/12077590.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/591413641?book_show_action=true">Apr 15, 2013</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Air" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Air" href="/user/show/12077590-air">Air</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer591413641" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13685469936075038360">This play is really funny, if you over look the usual sexism of the time. It is truly different than anything else I have ever read from this time. It isn&apos;t over religious, isn&apos;t hard to read or hard to follow. It is a quick read and I highly suggest it for anyone studying Theatre. </span>
  <span id="freeText13685469936075038360" style="display:none">This play is really funny, if you over look the usual sexism of the time. It is truly different than anything else I have ever read from this time. It isn't over religious, isn't hard to read or hard to follow. It is a quick read and I highly suggest it for anyone studying Theatre. </span>
